::Kluster::

Kluster looks from Phobia to Hot Rod. "If you'd exuse me for a minute," he 
says to Phobia, waking out of the room. He turns to Hot Rod as the door 
closes.

"I'm here," he says to Hot Rod, "What's the matter?"
